▁also ▁, ▁minamoto ▁no ▁yoriie ▁was ▁his ▁heir ▁and ▁right ▁away ▁was ▁appointed ▁to ▁sakone ▁no ▁chujo ▁, ▁and ▁then ▁saemon ▁no ▁kami ▁, ▁and ▁was ▁proclaimed ▁seii ▁taishogun ▁3 ▁years ▁later ▁.
▁then ▁at ▁the ▁time ▁of ▁the ▁hiki ▁yoshikazu ▁incident ▁, ▁the ▁succession ▁of ▁the ▁positions ▁of ▁sotsu ibushi ▁and ▁soj ito ▁were ▁in ▁question ▁, ▁and ▁the ▁shogun ▁posts ▁were ▁not ▁involved ▁.
